<h3>Admission Criteria</h3>
<p>PMSM (with an HR concentration) welcomes applications from well-rounded individuals with minimum 2 years’ work experience who bring unique insight to the classroom learning environment and team experience.</p>
<p>Follow these steps to apply:</p>
<ol>
<li>Complete the online application and remit the $30 application fee.</li>
    <li>Submit all required documents, including official undergraduate transcripts, GMAT or GRE test scores, three letters of recommendation, and a career goal statement outlining your 5- and 10-year objectives, and explaining how the PMSM/HR program will assist you in obtaining these goals.
</li>
    <li>Schedule an interview with the PMSM Admissions Committee.</li>
</ol>

		                </div>
	                </div>
