<h3>Tuition Schedule</h3>
<p>The tuition for the PMSM program is an all-inclusive package. It covers all tuition costs, textbooks, orientation, parking during class times, class shirt, lifetime membership to the UCF Alumni Association, and all administrative fees. This fee applies to Florida residents only. Non-Florida residents should contact the Executive Development Center to determine the current out-of-state tuition rate for the PMSM program.</p>
<p>Many employers offer PMSM reimbursement packages. Please check with your employer to determine the availability of financial assistance.</p>
<p>Participants of the PMSM program are often eligible for financial aid. Contact UCF’s Financial Aid department for more information.</p>

<p>View the current PMSM tuition schedule.</p> 
